<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8"/>
	<title>使用优惠券</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no;" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
	<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="email=no" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/master.css" />
</head>
<body>
	<header>
		<a href="fill.html" class="x-close">x</a>
		<h1>使用优惠券</h1>
	</header>
	<section class="container fill-coupon">
		<div class="fill-coupon-tab"><span class="select-coupon-tab"><em class="tab-red">选择可用现金券<i class="color">(3)</i></em></span><span class="hand-coupon-tab"><em>手动输入现金券号</em></span></div>
		<ul class="select-coupon">
			<li class="clearfix coupon-off">
				<div class="fl">全国批发券DB3242<br/>剩余<i class="coupon-surplus">100</i>次已用12次 </div><div class="fr">抵扣100元 <br/>满100元可用</div><div class="coupon-change"><i class="coupon-minus">&minus;</i><input type="tel" value="99" readonly="readonly"/><i class="coupon-plus">+</i></div>
			</li>
			<li class="clearfix  coupon-off coupon-on">
				<div class="fl">全国批发券DB3242<br/>剩余<i class="coupon-surplus">100</i>次已用12次 </div><div class="fr">抵扣100元 <br/>满100元可用</div><div class="coupon-change"><i class="coupon-minus">&minus;</i><input type="tel" value="1" readonly="readonly"/><i class="coupon-plus">+</i></div>
			</li>
			<li class="clearfix coupon-off-gray">
				<div class="fl">全国批发券DB3242<br/>剩余<i class="coupon-surplus">100</i>次已用12次 </div><div class="fr">抵扣100元 <br/>满100元可用</div><div class="coupon-change"><i class="coupon-minus">&minus;</i><input type="tel" value="1" readonly="readonly"/><i class="coupon-plus">+</i></div>
			</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="fill-coupon-use hidden">
			<div class="coupon-use-text">现金卷号：</div><input type="text" placeholder="请输入"/><div class="coupon-use-x hidden">&nbsp;</div>
		</div>
		<div class="wrap">
			<p class="f-16 color test-ok hidden">验证通过可抵扣20.00元</p>
			<p class="f-16 color test-fail hidden">验证失败，请确认输入券号是否有效</p>
			<p class="f-16 color test-used hidden">很抱歉，该卷号已使用!</p>
			<p class="coupon-pa">最大可用100元全国批发券，10元本地批发券；</p>
			<a href="#" class="btn-red coupon-sure">使用</a>
			<a href="#" class="btn-red coupon-test-btn hidden">验证</a>
			<a href="#" class="btn-red coupon-finish-btn hidden">完成</a>
		</div>
	</section>
	<div class="masker hidden"></div>
	<div class="popup hidden"><p>很抱歉，您购物车的商品不可使用该<br/>金额的优惠券！</p><a href="javascript:;" class="btn-red popup-btn">确定</a></div>
</body>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/lib/zepto.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common/setting.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/common/common.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/wholesale/coupon.js"></script>
</html>